xwdtps_g.c File Reference

#include "xparameters.h"

Variables

XWdtPs_Config XWdtPs_ConfigTable [XPAR_XWDTPS_NUM_INSTANCES]

Detailed Description

This file contains a table that specifies the configuration of the watchdog timer devices in the system. Each device should have an entry in the table.

 {
        {
                XPAR_XWDTPS_0_DEVICE_ID,
                XPAR_XWDTPS_0_BASEADDR
        }

This table contains configuration information for each watchdog timer device in the system.
